            #:return Image
            #:args (list '("x" "") 
                         '("y" "") 
                         '("width" "") 
                         '("height" "") 
                         '("img" ""))]{
    Crops @pyret{img} to the rectangle with the upper left at the point
    (x,y) and with width @pyret{width} and height @pyret{height}.
